en_144283_4	BIMSTEC has been established for countries located around the Bay of Bengal, with the aim of establishing Multi-Sectoral Technical & Economic Cooperation.
en_144283_5	Accordingly, President Maithripala Sirisena is to attend the summit held in Goa on the 15th and 16th of October.
